---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy · Pro Se Fair Play Mediation"
  description="How Pro Se Fair Play Mediation handles privacy and security — confidentiality of mediation sessions and infrastructure-level protections for the website."
>
  <!-- ========================== HEADER ========================== -->
  <header class="legal-header">
    <div class="container legal-header-inner">
      <p class="kicker reveal reveal-d1">
        <a href="/" class="back-link">
          <span class="arrow-left" aria-hidden="true">←</span>
          Home
        </a>
        <span class="kicker-sep" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
        Legal
      </p>
      <h1 class="display legal-title reveal reveal-d2">
        Privacy &amp; <span class="display-italic">Confidentiality</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="lede reveal reveal-d3">
        How your mediation, your communications, and your data are kept
        private — both in session and in transit.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- ========================== BODY ========================== -->
  <section class="legal-body">
    <div class="container-narrow legal-prose">
      <h2 class="display section-h2">Confidentiality of Mediation</h2>
      <p>
        Mediation is private. Discussions, negotiations, and potential
        resolutions remain confidential, unlike court proceedings which
        are part of the public record.
      </p>
      <p>
        Confidentiality in Florida mediation is defined by Chapter
        44 of the Florida Statutes and the Florida Supreme Court Rules
        for Certified and Court-Appointed Mediators. Anything shared with
        the mediator in session, except in narrow circumstances required
        by law, stays in the room. See Florida Statutes 44.406 and 44.407.
      </p>

      <h2 class="display section-h2">Website Security</h2>
      <p>
        This website is hosted on Cloudflare's global network, which
        provides several layers of security.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>HTTPS encryption everywhere</strong> — all traffic
          between your browser and this site is encrypted with TLS, with
          certificates auto-renewed.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>No personal data stored on the website itself</strong>
          — there is no database, and nothing to be stolen.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        That said, no internet transmission can be guaranteed 100% secure.
        Information you share with us through any online channel is shared
        at your own risk, with reasonable industry-standard protections
        in place.
      </p>

      <h2 class="display section-h2">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        We collect only the information you provide voluntarily:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Information submitted when booking a consultation (name, email, phone, brief description of your situation, conflict-check details)</li>
        <li>Email correspondence you initiate with us</li>
        <li>Standard server logs (IP address, browser type) for security and routine operation</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        We do not sell your information. We do not share it with third
        parties except as necessary to provide our services such as scheduling and payment processing.
      </p>

      <h2 class="display section-h2">Questions</h2>
      <p>
        For questions about privacy or how your information is handled,
        email <a href="mailto:info@prosefairplaymediation.com">info@prosefairplaymediation.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-header {
    position: relative;
    padding-block: clamp(4rem, 6vw + 1rem, 6rem) clamp(2rem, 3vw, 3rem);
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%, rgba(196, 154, 75, 0.08), transparent 55%),
      var(--color-cream);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-divider);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .legal-header-inner { position: relative; max-width: 64rem; }
  .back-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-gold-deep);
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .back-link:hover { color: var(--color-navy); }
  .arrow-left { transition: transform 0.3s var(--ease-out); }
  .back-link:hover .arrow-left { transform: translateX(-3px); }
  .kicker-sep { color: var(--color-divider); margin-inline: 0.4rem; }
  .legal-title {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: var(--step-5);
    line-height: 1.02;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .legal-title .display-italic {
    color: var(--color-gold-deep);
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .legal-header .lede {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .legal-body {
    padding-block: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-3xl);
    background: var(--color-cream);
  }
  .legal-prose {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--step-1);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
  }
  .legal-prose p + p { margin-top: 1.25rem; }
  .legal-prose strong { color: var(--color-navy); font-weight: 600; }
  .legal-prose ul {
    margin-block: 1.25rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.65rem;
  }
  .legal-prose li {
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .legal-prose a {
    color: var(--color-navy);
    background-image: linear-gradient(var(--color-gold), var(--color-gold));
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: 100% 1px;
    background-position: 0 92%;
  }
  .legal-prose a:hover { color: var(--color-gold-deep); }

  .section-h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: var(--step-3);
    color: var(--color-navy);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    font-weight: 400;
    padding-top: 1.25rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-divider);
    position: relative;
  }
  .section-h2::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: -1px; left: 0;
    width: 2.5rem; height: 1px;
    background: var(--color-gold);
  }
  .section-h2:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 0;
    padding-top: 0;
    border-top: 0;
  }
  .section-h2:first-of-type::before {
    display: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .legal-title { font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 1.8rem + 3vw, 3.5rem); }
    .section-h2 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 1.2rem + 2vw, 2.25rem); }
  }
</style>
